    <h1>{`Dai Credit System`}</h1>
    <h3>{`A permissionless loan facility for issuing the Dai stablecoin`}</h3>
    <p>{`The Dai Credit System allows users to self-issue Dai-denominated loans against collateral deposited into smart contract-based escrow. `}</p>
